replies.body:
While they're at it they are nerfing the passive on {{item:3153}} because {{champion:96}} would abuse it ridiculously hard thanks to his new W letting him get 5.0 attack speed.

...which completely ruins it for {{champion:11}} {{champion:23}} {{champion:24}} {{champion:39}}. They have to nerf the shit out of a core item on 4 champions just because one ADC would be broken if it remained in it's current state. I love Koggie but he shouldn't get special treatment, why they couldn't just make it 8% for melees and 6% for ranged is beyond me.

Not to mention the new {{item:3078}} changes shoehorning it into an item that any ADC can buy at the cost of the champions that don't scale with crit. I would have preferred they created a new Sheen item with a spellblade that scales with bonus AD instead of reworking the core damage item for so many fighters. Admittedly ADC itemization was too linear but that's no excuse to rework Triforce in a way that ruins it for {{champion:75}} {{champion:77}} {{champion:254}} {{champion:120}}
